data.description: *Seller is offering $3,000 in closing cost with acceptable offer!!* Captivating three-bedroom, two-bathroom home in Ardmore Village. This property boasts numerous updates, including pristine flooring and elegant granite countertops in the kitchen. Enjoy the convenience of bluetooth lighting in both bathrooms and a master bedroom adorned with a chandelier that doubles as a fan. (fandelier) The fenced backyard, complete with a deck, pool, and hot tub, creates an inviting oasis, perfect for entertaining. Don't miss out on this ideal blend of modern comfort and outdoor allure. Your perfect home awaits!
